Source: NZ Journal of Science & Technology
Author:
Vol / Page: 6/82
Edition:
Quote: <i>Apteryx haasti</i> Potts. Great Grey Kiwi; Roa. Judging from the scanty reports, this is still the rarest of the three species of <i>Apteryx</i>. Mr. R. S. Sutherland gives one South Island locality where it may be occasionally seen.
Notes: Myers Endemic Birds

